<br>
Anyone have any suggestions for equipment upgrades for my level 52 mage? He is my highest level character at the moment... so please keep any ideas in his range please. Thanks a lot in advance! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=deelit60>Deelit60</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 80<br> <font color=#333333>(12/21/02 9:31:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1123.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need suggestions for equipment upgrades</span><hr size=1> Your head, arms, and gloves would all get useful upgrades from apothic armor, and your robe too but not as much as the others.<br>
<br>
Coldain shawl quests for your shoulders are relatively easy if you've done any tradeskills, and if not pauldrons of the witness are probably becoming pretty cheap in the bazaar about now.<br>
<br>
Your feet are fine but you could easily upgrade to coldain skin boots, either by paying or by giant ally-ing.<br>
<br>
The biggest thing is the orb of tashan, which I don't know why you're wielding. There's any number of cheap 1hb which give mana and int and the effect from tishan isn't really needed.<br>
<br>
52 is a little low to do the crypt in sebilis but if a group will take you the hiero cloak drops and would be a good upgrade for you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gadevanshade>Gade VanShade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#333333>(12/21/02 6:27:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1123.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need suggestions for equipment upgrades</span><hr size=1> Alright... thanks for the suggestions <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
