<br>
Earring of the Solstice is also a great upgrade if you have a guild that can do the tradeskills -- or the coin to purchase the items yourself.  It's worth it alone for the Flowing Thought 1!<br>
<br>
Phenocryst Focus is a very easy quest to do.  You just need a group of 50+ at the end to kill a couple of giants.  The rest of the quest you can do yourself.<br>
<br>
/agree on the Coldain Prayer Shawl quests.  You can get the first two very easily without any tradeskills.  The thrid one will also get you a very nice range item along with the shawl.  The tradeskills needed for the third and fourth shawl shouldn't cost you too much time/coin either.<br>
<br>
Anyway, just my 2cp.  Good luck to you!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
