</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=variathemage>Varia the mage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 118<br> <font color=#333333>(12/22/02 10:53:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1123.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need suggestions for equipment upgrades</span><hr size=1> You didn't say if you are in a guild or good friends with one.  It would have helped a bit, but no worries.<br>
<br>
Apothic would be a nice upgrade for all of your slots other than wrists and maybe boots.  Thurgadin quest armor would also be nice and you could probably camp that area in Kael with one group.<br>
<br>
Face: An enshrouded veil would serve you well.  They are fairly inexpensive to buy in the bazaar.  Very common drop in the South wing of Howling Stones, if you would rather camp it.<br>
<br>
Head: I believe it is called a runed cowl.  It drops off a named caster undead froglok near the executioner in Lower Guk.<br>
<br>
Shawl: The coldain shawl quests aren't that difficult to start off.  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/quests/intro.htm" target="top">EQTrader</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> is a good site to look at for info on the quests.<br>
<br>
Primary: A glowing black stone, pheno focus crystal, or a cone of the mystics would all be nice upgrades.<br>
<br>
Secondary: Your stein isn't a bad item.  If you have a shaman friend looking to do the shammy epic, you might ask if you can tag along to help.  Many like to do the final fight with mage 49 fire pets and clerics healing them.  One of the steps in the quest requires you to kill Neh'Ashiir and his common drop is the ornate runed shield.  If you do get this shield and haven't upgraded your primary, I'd put your stein in the primary slot.<br>
<br>
There are a ton of other threads dealing with item upgrades for mages around your level.  You might want to use the search feature (next to mark all forums read) so you can get some other ideas. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=108671">Varia Darselai</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> Arch Convoker</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showPrevMessage?topicID=1123.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showNextMessage?topicID=1123.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1123.topic&index=4><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.threadControl?topicID=1123.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1123.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1123.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowerannouncements">Administration<option value="themagicianstowergeneral">General<option value="themagicianstowerfrm